YafaRay uses CMake for the building process in Linux, Windows and MacOSX systems.

See directory "building" for example procedures to build YafaRay

Dependencies:
  Mandatory:
    >=zlib-1.2.8
    >=libxml2-2.9.1
    >=boost-1.5.8
  Optional, depending on options selected in CMake:
    >=opencv-3.1.0
    >=freetype-2.4.0
    >=libpng-1.2.56
    >=jpeg-6b
    >=tiff-4.0.3
    >=ilmbase-2.2.0
    >=openexr-2.2.0
    >=python-3.5
    >=ruby-2.2
    >=qt-4.8
    
